Detecting or interacting with dreams isn't possible - there's no technology that can read dream content or interface software with the sleeping brain.

**However**, I can create something thematically similar - objects that interact with other users' **"dream worlds"** (private instances they've created):

```holoscript
scene DreamNetwork @networked {

