      data: Object.entries(RECIPES)

      template RecipeItem {
        panel {
          size: [1, 0.2]
          style: {
            background: canCraft(item[0]) ? '#2a4a2e' : '#4a2a2e'
            borderRadius: 4
            margin: 4
          }

          text Name {
            position: [0.1, 0.7, 0]
            content: '{ITEM_DATABASE[item[1].result.item].name}'
            color: '#FFFFFF'
            fontSize: 12
          }

          text Materials {
            position: [0.1, 0.3, 0]
            content: formatMaterials(item[1].materials)
            color: '#888888'
            fontSize: 9
          }

          button Craft {
            position: [0.85, 0.5, 0]
            size: [0.25, 0.6]
            text: 'Craft'
            enabled: canCraft(item[0])
            on click {
              call craftItem(item[0])
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  // Keybinds
  on key 'I' {
    toggle InventoryPanel.visible
  }

  on key 'C' {
    toggle CraftingPanel.visible
  }

  // Helper
  function formatMaterials(materials) {
    return Object.entries(materials)
      .map(([id, count]) => '{ITEM_DATABASE[id]?.name}: {getItemCount(id)}/{count}')
      .join(', ')
  }
}
```

**Features included**:
- **Item system**: Rarities with stat multipliers, equipment slots, stackables
- **Inventory grid**: 24 slots with drag-drop, tooltips, context menus
- **Equipment**: 5 slots with stat recalculation on equip/unequip
- **Consumables**: Health/mana potions with use effects
- **Crafting**: Recipe-based with material checking
- **Selling**: Gold-based economy with sell values
- **UI**: Polished panels with proper styling and interactions

